OL,3,CSpeaker says he gave information to
OL,4,Cpolice about Lord Mandelson ahead of
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle said
OL,8,Fhe passed information to the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police about Lord Peter
OL,10,FMandelson, after the peer claimed
OL,11,F"baseless suggestions" he was a flight
OL,12,Frisk had led to his arrest this week.
OL,14,FIn a statement in Parliament on
OL,15,FWednesday morning, Sir Lindsay said he
OL,16,Fwanted to confirm media reports that
OL,17,Fhe was the source of the information,
OL,18,Fwhich Lord Mandelson claims was the
OL,19,Freason for his arrest, to "prevent any
OL,20,Finaccurate speculation".
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
