CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772025561
OL,3,CSpeaker says he gave information to
OL,4,Cpolice about Lord Mandelson ahead of
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FThe Times reported that Hoyle told
OL,8,Fofficers he had been informed the peer
OL,9,Fwas allegedly planning to flee Britain
OL,10,Ffor the British Virgin Islands.
OL,12,FSir Lindsay did not confirm what
OL,13,Finformation he had passed to the
OL,14,Fpolice in his statement, but
OL,15,Freferenced "comments in the media
OL,16,Fregarding the arrest of Lord
OL,17,FMandelson".
OL,19,FThe statement said: "Members will be
OL,20,Faware of comments in the media
OL,21,Fregarding the arrest of Lord Mandelson.
OL,26,@{D@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772025561
OL,3,CSpeaker says he gave information to
OL,4,Cpolice about Lord Mandelson ahead of
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,F"To prevent any inaccurate speculation
OL,8,FI'd like to confirm that, upon receipt
OL,9,Fof information, that I felt it was
OL,10,Frelevant I pass this on to the
OL,11,FMetropolitan Police in good faith, as
OL,12,Fis my duty and responsibility.
OL,14,F"It is regrettable this rapidly ended
OL,15,Fin the media.
OL,17,F"As this is a live investigation,
OL,18,Fmembers will understand... it would
OL,19,Fnot be appropriate to make any further
OL,20,Fcomment, and I'd like to caution
OL,21,Fmembers from doing so."
