OL,3,CSpeaker says he gave information to
OL,4,Cpolice about Lord Mandelson ahead of
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FLord Mandelson was released on bail in
OL,8,Fthe early hours of Tuesday after his
OL,9,Farrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,10,Fpublic office.
OL,12,FThe former Labour minister has been
OL,13,Faccused of passing highly sensitive
OL,14,Fgovernment information to paedophile
OL,15,Ffinancier Jeffrey Epstein during his
OL,16,Ftime as business secretary under
OL,17,Fformer prime minister Gordon Brown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
