OL,3,CSpeaker says he gave information to
OL,4,Cpolice about Lord Mandelson ahead of
OL,5,Carrest
OL,7,FLord Mandelson was sacked as US
OL,8,Fambassador in September after Downing
OL,9,FStreet said fresh revelations about
OL,10,Fhis relationship with Epstein had
OL,11,Femerged.
OL,13,FHe resigned from the House of Lords
OL,14,Fearlier this month, following the
OL,15,Frelease of the so-called Epstein
OL,16,Ffiles. However, due to parliamentary
OL,17,Fprocedure, he retains his title.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
